pageTitle: Splash Seafood Bar & Grill - Des Moines Seafood Restaurant
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {6608=The idea for Splash was given birth on the water in 1998 by an avid Key’s fisherman, Bruce Gerleman. His fishing expeditions took him all over the Florida Keys where he discovered exotic meals cooked by the ‘locals’. Inspired by the varied styles and flavors of the food, he began gathering recipes from Key West, Islamorada and Key Largo. In the tradition of this island-style cooking, Splash was created.}
